<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        p {
            max-width: 500px;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: left;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .thank-you-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: forestgreen;
        }
        .feedback{
          width: 100%%;
          height: 200px;
          font-size: 18px;
        }
        .submit-button{
          background: forestgreen;
          font-size: 24px;
          width: 100%%;
          height: 40px;
          font-weight: bold;
          border: none;
          color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 style="color: forestgreen">We are so happy for you answer!</h1>
	<br>
    <p>Our main goal as a company is to make happy customers.</p>
	<br>
	<p>If you are seeing this message, it means that we accomplished that goal! :D</p>
	<h2>Want to share a positive feedback for our team? Go ahead!</h2>
	
	<form action="/send-feedback" method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="ticket" value=<%= ticket %> />
	  <div>
	    <textarea name="feedback" class="feedback" type="text" placeholder="Tell us what you loved about our company and click 'Submit'" rows="20"></textarea>
	  </div>
	  <div>
	    <button class="submit-button" type="submit">Submit</button>
	  </div>
	</form>
</body>
</html>
